main event: Six jets had 28 minutes to see and track a UFO. The object was described as having a variable shape, color, size, and speed, and was tracked on radar. The object disappeared very rapidly at various times.
interesting points: The object was tracked on radar.
The object had a variable shape, color, size, and speed.
The object disappeared very rapidly at various times.
Multiple jets were able to visually observe and track the object.
